### =================== BRAND CRUD OPERATIONS ===================

### 1. Create a new Brand
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/brands
{{authHeader}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Apple",
  "description": "Technology company known for iPhone and Mac computers",
  "website": "https://www.apple.com",
  "logoUrl": "https://example.com/logos/apple.png",
  "isActive": true
}

### 2. Create another Brand
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/brands
{{authHeader}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dickess",
  "description": "Fuck you momom",
  "website": "https://www.samsung.com",
  "isActive": true
}

### 3. Create Brand with minimal data
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/brands
{{authHeader}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Generic Brand",
  "isActive": true
}

### 4. Get all Brands (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/brands?page=0&size=20&sortBy=name&sortDir=asc
{{authHeader}}

### 5. Get Brands with search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/brands?search=samsung&active=true&page=0&size=10
{{authHeader}}

### 6. Get Active Brands only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/brands?active=true&page=0&size=50
{{authHeader}}

### 7. Get Inactive Brands only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/brands?active=false&page=0&size=20
{{authHeader}}

### 8. Get all Active Brands (no pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/brands/active
{{authHeader}}

### 9. Get Active Brands List (alternative endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/brands/active/list
{{authHeader}}

### 10. Get a specific Brand by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/brands/2
{{authHeader}}

### 11. Update a Brand
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/brands/1
{{authHeader}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Apple Inc.",
  "description": "Updated description: Apple is an American multinational technology company",
  "website": "https://www.apple.com/updated",
  "logoUrl": "https://example.com/logos/apple-updated.png"
}

### 12. Deactivate a Brand (soft delete)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/brands/1
{{authHeader}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": false
}

### 13. Reactivate a Brand
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/brands/1
{{authHeader}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": true
}

### 14. Soft Delete a Brand
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/brands/2
{{authHeader}}

